{"tid":816700,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾一百萬加泰人上街爭獨立","createTime":"2018-09-13T02:04:41.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T11:31:02.000Z","uid":184679,"like":37,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"e2215fbbc7efdbd6b89347930fc23e62137bbfab","tid":816700,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:04:41.000Z","msg":"【星島日報報道】西班牙加泰隆尼亞獨立公投被中央拒認投票結果後將近一周年，逾一百萬民眾趁周二加泰「民族紀念日」，在巴塞隆拿上街示威，爭取脫離西班牙獨立。示威人龍延綿數公里，民眾揮動象徵加泰獨立的旗幟，打響鑼敲，高呼獨立及舉起「自由」的標語。他們是響應加泰自治政府主席托拉及其前任普伊格蒙特的號召上街。加泰去年十月一日舉行獨立公投，通過脫離西班牙，但中央政府拒絕承認結果，普伊格德蒙特流亡海外，目前仍有九人被囚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E7%88%AD%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-221116466.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%2599%25BE%25E8%2590%25AC%25E5%258A%25A0%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25B8%258A%25E8%25A1%2597%25E7%2588%25AD%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B-221116466.html&d=qpIW4utTcIAj%2BOeL76mdrUkviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=14b030ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%99%BE%E8%90%AC%E5%8A%A0%E6%B3%B0%E4%BA%BA%E4%B8%8A%E8%A1%97%E7%88%AD%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B-221116466.html</a>"},{"pid":"e8edc4db3d2332d5b60cd6be0e54eeb4ff621068","tid":816700,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"美國唔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65d58e158c7e5479ab1588e6b0c83033f6d137a","tid":816700,"uid":37733,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e8edc4db3d2332d5b60cd6be0e54eeb4ff621068","tid":816700,"uid":5649,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:21:33.000Z","msg":"美國唔支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-13T02:30:32.000Z","msg":"我地香港有學獨聯<br />\n吹雞都吹到100人"},{"pid":"dc6694ae1e29d079e47ce1cc6c5107b5acf84505","tid":816700,"uid":184679,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b65d58e158c7e5479ab1588